net.uniform.html.validators

Class NumericValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.uniform.html.validators.NumericValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validator<Element>

    public class NumericValidator
extends Object
implements Validator<Element>
    Validator for any single-value numeric input. It supports:
    • Allowing decimals or not
    • A minimum allowed value (inclusive or not)
    • A maximum allowed value (inclusive or not)
    Author:
    Eduardo Ramos
